IronBee is not ready for users yet.  Currently it is available in a technology preview.  To build this code:

Get the code:

  git clone git://github.com/ironbee/ironbee.git

Update code from submodules:

  cd ironbee
  git submodule init
  git submodule update

Build:

  ./autogen.sh
  ./configure
  make
  make check
  sudo make install

Configure:

  # NOTE: Java required
  make manual

  And then read the manual in docs/docbook/manual/output/

If you would like to take a look at the developer docs, then:

  # NOTE: doxygen and graphviz required
  make doxygen

  And take a look at those docs in docs/doxygen/html/index.html

